title: CreativeMarket - Master UI Kit
description:
About

Master.UI Kit is a great package of components necessary for the creation of the modern web. All in one PSD file allows easy work. Pictures in components can be easily changed just a few clicks using smart objects. Modern colors and typography determine a high level. This product was created for anyone who has ideas for websites but has no concept designed components. Now you can compose ;)

What is the content of the file.

Master.UI Kit PSD file contains a number of web components which can easily create a complete website. Each component is added to the group. Inside are all the parts that you can edit at any time. You can change colors, text, images, layer effects. Everything you have in one place from where easy to copy just what you need.

Include components

    Blockquote
    Team
    Lists
    Testimonial
    Radio Buttons
    Switches
    Checkboxes
    Controls
    Scroll bars
    Typography
    Search

    Services
